#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-18-pre-commit-autoupdate-ci.rst:8
msgid "pre-commit フックを GitHub Actions で自動更新する"
msgstr "Automatically update pre-commit hooks with GitHub Actions"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-18-pre-commit-autoupdate-ci.rst:10
msgid ""
"`pre-commit autoupdate` を定期的に自動実行し、フックのバージョン更新PRを GitHub Actions "
"経由で作成する仕組みを紹介します。"
msgstr ""
"We will introduce a mechanism to automatically execute `pre-commit "
"autoupdate` periodically and create a hook version update PR via GitHub "
"Actions."

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-18-pre-commit-autoupdate-ci.rst:17
msgid "自動更新導入の目的"
msgstr "Purpose of introducing automatic updates"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-18-pre-commit-autoupdate-ci.rst:19
msgid "フックのバージョンは手動更新しないと古くなる"
msgstr "Hook versions become outdated unless manually updated"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-18-pre-commit-autoupdate-ci.rst:20
msgid "セキュリティパッチや仕様変更を取り込みたい"
msgstr "I want to incorporate security patches and specification changes"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-18-pre-commit-autoupdate-ci.rst:21
msgid "ローカルで `pre-commit` を使っていないユーザの変更にも効く"
msgstr ""
"Also works for changes made by users who are not using `pre-commit` locally."

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-18-pre-commit-autoupdate-ci.rst:24
msgid "設定ファイル例"
msgstr "Configuration file example"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-18-pre-commit-autoupdate-ci.rst:26
msgid "以下を ``.github/workflows/pre-commit-autoupdate.yml`` に配置します："
msgstr ""
"Place the following in ``.github/workflows/pre-commit-autoupdate.yml``:"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-18-pre-commit-autoupdate-ci.rst:70
msgid "注意点と推奨運用"
msgstr "Points to note and recommended operations"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-18-pre-commit-autoupdate-ci.rst:72
msgid "生成されたPRは手動でレビュー＆マージ"
msgstr "Manually review and merge generated PRs"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-18-pre-commit-autoupdate-ci.rst:73
msgid "差分を確認して問題なければ取り込む"
msgstr "Check the difference and import if there are no problems"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-18-pre-commit-autoupdate-ci.rst:74
msgid "`pre-commit run --all-files` で CI による整合性チェックを追加すると安全"
msgstr ""
"It is safe to add consistency checks by CI with `pre-commit run --all-files`"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-18-pre-commit-autoupdate-ci.rst:77
msgid "おわりに"
msgstr "Conclusion"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-18-pre-commit-autoupdate-ci.rst:79
msgid "自動更新の仕組みを組み込んでおくことで、運用コストを下げつつ、継続的にクリーンな開発環境を保つことができます。"
msgstr ""
"By incorporating an automatic update mechanism, you can continuously "
"maintain a clean development environment while lowering operational costs."

